{"id":406543743,"lang":"java","time":"8 months, 3 weeks","timestamp":1602245482,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"8 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/406543743/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"39.1 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int lengthOfLongestSubstring(String s) {\n        int ans = 0;\n        int left = 0;\n        HashMap<Character, Integer> count = new HashMap<>();\n        for (int i = 0; i < s.length(); i++) {\n            char ch = s.charAt(i);\n            while (count.getOrDefault(ch, 0) > 0) count.merge(s.charAt(left++), -1, Integer::sum);\n            count.merge(ch, 1, Integer::sum);\n            ans = Math.max(ans, i - left + 1);\n        }\n        return ans;\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters"}
